I'm sorry to hear that your ads were disapproved. Could you please provide more details about the reason given for the disapproval? This will help me assist you better.

No worries! Ad rejection reasons can vary. I recommend checking your email for any specific details from Ad Support regarding the disapproval. Additionally, you can review our advertising policy to ensure your ads comply with our guidelines. You can find more information here: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next). If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!
